markets.title: Will above 599999 jobs be added in February 2023?
markets.subtitle: 600,000 or above
markets.rules_primary: If the increase in total non-farm payroll employment is above 599999 as reported by the Bureau of Labor Statistics Monthly Employment Situation Report for the month of February 2023, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The market closes at 8:25 AM ET on the expected date of the data release. The market expires at the sooner of the first 10:00 AM following the release of the data, or two weeks after the scheduled release of the data.
